Name: Delivery in Space
About the game: Your goal is to successfully reach the planets to make deliveries. You need to observe the best way to get to your destination using our card-based movement system to move the spaceship. Wormholes, nebulas and solar storms will not stop you on this journey! Travel across the galaxy, admire the wonders of outer space and be careful not to be swallowed by a black hole!
